Stargazers Cosmic Watchlist

2024-2025

Premium watchlist for anime, movies, TV, and games with smart stats, TMDB enrichment, and server-first architecture.

Next.js
TypeScript
cosmic-ui
Drizzle

About

A server-first CRUD watchlist application featuring Google OAuth, AI-powered recommendations via TMDB, comprehensive statistics (runtime totals, completion rates, heatmaps), and beautiful glassy UI. Built with cosmic-ui design system, Drizzle ORM for type-safe database operations, and Next.js Server Actions for mutations.
